Package ch.ethz.inspire.emod.gui.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BarChart
    creates bar chart. the chart is a singleton implementation
    ConfigCheckResultGUI  
    ConfigStatusGUI
    Graphical display of the configuration status of - the machine set-up (M) - the simulation configuration (S) - the process settings (P)
    ConsumerData
    holds data read from simulation output file.
    LineChart
    creates a chart from active ConsumerData objects. currently only one chart can be drawn.
    MachineComponentComposite  
    MachineComponentHandler
    Handler class for machine component GUIs
    MaterialHandler
    Handler Class for material GUIs
    ProgressbarGUI
    Implements the display of a process by its name and current status (progressbar).
    ShowButtons
    Class to handle which buttons are to be displayed in a config gui Possible buttons are: - OK - RESET - CANCEL
    StackedAreaChart  
    TableUtils
    Implements general table functions for SWT Tables
